### **4. main_RealTimePulseChart**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes real-time numeric streams with smooth scrolling and live metrics display.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimePulseChart - Live Metric Stream Visualizer

RealTimePulseChart displays streaming values in a responsive chart ideal for dashboards and system monitoring.

## Features
- Auto-updating line chart  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Matplotlib-powered  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_RealTimePulseChart.git
cd main_RealTimePulseChart
python visualize.py
